<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>登录 - 书签管理器</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/tailwind.generated.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/app.css" />
  <script>
    (function () {
      var theme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
      if (theme === 'dark') {
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
      } else if (theme === 'light') {
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
      }
    })();
  </script>
</head>

<body class="auth-page login-page" data-testid="login-page">
  <main class="page-shell page-shell--auth">
    <div class="auth-layout">
      <section class="auth-card login-card" aria-labelledby="login-title">
        <div class="auth-card__header">
          <div class="auth-card__intro">
            <div class="auth-eyebrow">🔐 安全登录</div>
            <h1 id="login-title" class="auth-title">登录到书签管理器</h1>
            <p class="auth-subtitle">继续访问你的自托管书签工作台，管理收藏、检查任务、网页快照与 AI 整理流程。</p>
          </div>
          <button id="theme-toggle" type="button" class="btn-secondary btn-sm auth-theme-toggle"
            data-testid="login-theme-toggle" aria-label="切换主题">🌙</button>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="auth-error mt-6" role="alert" data-testid="login-error">
            <div class="auth-error__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</div>
            <div>
              <div class="auth-error__title">登录失败</div>
              <div><%= error %></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="post" action="/login" class="section-stack auth-form mt-6" data-testid="login-form">
          <label class="form-field">
            <span class="form-label">用户名</span>
            <input type="text" name="username" required autofocus autocomplete="username" class="form-control"
              placeholder="请输入用户名" aria-label="请输入用户名" data-testid="login-username-input" />
            <span class="form-hint">输入管理员用户名继续。</span>
          </label>

          <label class="form-field">
            <span class="form-label">密码</span>
            <input type="password" name="password" required autocomplete="current-password" class="form-control"
              placeholder="请输入密码" aria-label="请输入密码" data-testid="login-password-input" />
            <span class="form-hint">支持浏览器自动填充当前站点密码。</span>
          </label>

          <div class="auth-form__meta">
            <label for="remember" class="remember-field" data-testid="login-remember-toggle">
              <input type="checkbox" name="remember" id="remember" />
              <span>记住我（7天内免登录）</span>
            </label>
            <div class="auth-inline-note">连续失败 10 次后，当前 IP 会被锁定 30 分钟。</div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary btn-lg w-full justify-center" data-testid="login-submit">登录</button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-footer-note">
          登录页会自动沿用你上次使用的主题偏好；登录成功后会直接返回书签工作台。
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="auth-showcase" aria-label="产品概览">
        <div class="auth-showcase__badge">Self-hosted workspace</div>
        <h2 class="auth-showcase__title">一个入口，继续你的收藏整理流。</h2>
        <p class="auth-showcase__description">
          登录后即可回到同一套管理界面，继续分类导航、批量检查、任务追踪、快照归档与 AI 整理。
        </p>

        <div class="auth-stat-grid" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="auth-stat-card">
            <span class="auth-stat-card__title">收藏整理</span>
            <span class="auth-stat-card__meta">分类、搜索、批量操作保持连续。</span>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-stat-card">
            <span class="auth-stat-card__title">任务追踪</span>
            <span class="auth-stat-card__meta">导入、检查与整理状态可持续查看。</span>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-stat-card">
            <span class="auth-stat-card__title">快照留档</span>
            <span class="auth-stat-card__meta">网页归档与回看入口集中管理。</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-feature-list">
          <article class="auth-feature-card">
            <div class="auth-feature-card__title">更聚焦的首屏</div>
            <p class="auth-feature-card__desc">表单、错误反馈与主题切换统一到同一套设计语言，桌面端与移动端都更清晰。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="auth-feature-card">
            <div class="auth-feature-card__title">保持原有登录契约</div>
            <p class="auth-feature-card__desc">不改变 `/login` 提交字段、会话行为与静态资源加载方式，只重做视觉层与交互层。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="auth-feature-card">
            <div class="auth-feature-card__title">更自然的错误定位</div>
            <p class="auth-feature-card__desc">错误信息集中展示在表单上方，同时保留明确的输入提示与键盘友好结构。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    (function () {
      var btn = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
      if (!btn) return;
      var updateIcon = function () {
        var theme = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
        btn.textContent = theme === 'dark' ? '☀️' : '🌙';
      };
      updateIcon();
      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        var current = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
        var next = current === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
        localStorage.setItem('theme', next);
        updateIcon();
      });
    })();
  </script>
</body>

</html>
